{"tid":767121,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"無故勃起同無故妊娠元凶應該係香水??","createTime":"2018-08-04T08:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T08:14:58.000Z","uid":112557,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cebf3e179e36a6a09e69ac0d617599152c3f334a","tid":767121,"uid":112557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"岩岩搭車聞到香水,就諗起果段舊聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睹男子自慰要求換位　女攝影師遭聯合航空職員嘲笑 2018-07-23 <br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n26歲的帕斯科拉（Genevieve Pascolla），上月4日由希思路機場登機後便開始睡覺。當她醒來，發現左方的男乘客在毛毯下「自摸」，令她大感錯愕。<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n詎料機組人員之後拿此來開玩笑，問帕斯科拉：「你噴了甚麼<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>香水</ins></span></span>？」又指該名男乘客喝了一點酒。<br />\n搭車聞到香水有時真係有D頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/bknint-20180723040349053-0723_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180723%2Fbknint-20180723040349053-0723_17011_001.html&d=FNLUDaUGLpi5VR9P9Y2fJcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f8ce2557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/bknint-20180723040349053-0723_17011_001.html</a>"}]}